{"tid":2298955,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"立場姐姐：法院外的一件小事","createTime":"2020-11-24T11:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T12:09:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0f03c356b60c7351958b5d75df01046668ad33","tid":2298955,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"今日（23 日）令人沉重的事已經夠多了，講一件小事。<br />\n<br />\n在東區裁判法院大堂等王婆婆保釋下樓，突然聽到樓外有很大的動靜。只見到一架黑色囚車駛過，應該是剛剛在鄭紀航法官判決下，要遭受九個月牢獄的科大學生。<br />\n<br />\n囚車轉彎駛入東裁大門前的太安街，已靠向中線，突然轉角有幾個少年少女跑出，直奔馬路中央，完全不顧那是好幾線的行車路，用盡力氣衝向路中心，想要以腳步追上正在全速駛走的囚車。<br />\n<br />\n「手足！」「手足！」<br />\n<br />\n囚車恰巧停在燈位。飛奔的幾個少年終於能靠近，撲向囚車，用似乎完全感覺不到手掌疼痛的力度，拍打著車窗外的鐵欄。<br />\n<br />\n「撐住啊！」「撐住啊！」其中一個瘦弱少年，看來不過中一、二的年紀，是即使在抗爭現場也不常見到的，小孩。穿著校服、瘦到 oversize 的冷衫，還背著書包，整個人附在囚車上大叫。<br />\n<br />\n「你唔係一個人啊！記得保重身體啊！」<br />\n<br />\n囚車的車窗漆黑。他們的喊聲卻整條太安街都能聽見。<br />\n<br />\n隔了好多、好多個月，再次見到這種在馬路上肆意奔跑的姿態，竟覺目眩。車水馬龍突然被剎停，旁聽師們一往無前撲向冰冷機器的身姿，令日常的荒涼片刻消散。<br />\n彷彿整條馬路，整個城市，都是他們的。<br />\n<br />\n（如果這段小事足以感動你，那麼，相信你也會想，目下並非無事可做。）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n（標題為編輯所擬）<br />\n<br />\n作者 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%B6%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaN3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=40bdc1b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&h=558e7add\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%B6%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"776ec7e872c7a8cd70550ca289846d7ddb8698dd","tid":2298955,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"立腸新聞一律當鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eeb1073e66c9ce0d93cc9a0748ac52040ffd461","tid":2298955,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"776ec7e872c7a8cd70550ca289846d7ddb8698dd","tid":2298955,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"立腸新聞一律當鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"民陣個個岑子杰係乜水黎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e654f8711f63dfc0e4e371297f79a02b8a34d8d8","tid":2298955,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T12:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}